Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:53.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我一概不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:58.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}希望自己變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:01.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我許下這樣的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}彷彿那衝破黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:08.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}孤獨的晨星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:12.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}深深沉淪的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}脆弱不堪的自己
